de in humans." Diabetes Care 10 (1987): 683-6', 'Latanoprost, Apraclonidine, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Brimonidine, Levobunolol', 'Sorbitol, Caffeine, Edrophonium, Indocyanine green, Inulin, Hexaminolevulinate, Secretin human, Galactose, Corticorelin, Macimorelin, Folic acid, More', 1767369485);
